high_descs: Walk forward to the counter then turn right and walk to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the orange wine glass that's in front of you.
Take a couple steps to your left until you're in front of the microwave.
Warm the wine glass in the microwave then take it back out and close the door.
Take a small step to your right.
Put the wine glass on the edge of the counter .
anns.task_desc: Put a warm wine glass on the counter.

high_descs: move forward and turn right and move to the counter
pick up the cup  off of the sink
turn left and move forward and then turn right and face to the microwave
place the cup in the microwave and heat it up and then take it out
turn right and walk forward and then turn left and face towards the counter
place the cup on to the counter
anns.task_desc: Take the cup to the microwave and heat it up and after it is done place it on the counter.

high_descs: Walk ahead and veer right to the counter left of the sink.
Pick up the yellow cup on the counter.
Heat the cup in the microwave.
Place the cup on the counter, in front and to the right of the fork.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated cup on a counter.
